name: Corona Attack (Ayush Dutt)
description:
After the devastating effects of the corona virus on our Earth, the Corona virus spread to the space and became more dangerous and transformed from Covid-19 to Covid-30 and are again trying to attack our Earth. But this time they don't only want to affect us but also rule as to wear masks forever. So, you are chosen to defeat them from ruling us. Go and use your all efforts to defeat them... Download now...

Gameplay:

Things new in this game:

1.New spaceship color.

2.New weapons.

3.New Secret enemy.

4.New asteroid.

5.New Score and Kills display system to get a beautiful display.

Made by Ayush Dutt.
